Numbered Tabs is a small userChrome.js (http://userchromejs.mozdev.org/)
script that adds and maintains index numbers to tab labels in Firefox.


Installation
------------
Install the userChromeJS extension if not already installed.
Insert the contents of numberedTabs.uc.js into
[profiledir]/chrome/userChrome.js, creating the file if it
does not exist yet.
Restart Firefox.


